abstract: This journey has naturally led to the realization of how important it is to have voices within the community telling our stories instead of ones told about us.

abstract: The initial awkwardness when you FINALLY hear the correct pronouns without having to correct someone is intense- that validation you have been dying to get is suddenly dropped in your lap, and you freeze.
